{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/add-font-awesome-icons-to-our-buttons","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"bootstrap","demoType":null,"title":"Dodajte ikone Font Awesome na naše dugme","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Font Awesome je jednostavna biblioteka ikona. Ove ikone mogu biti web fontovi ili vektorske crteže. One su tretirane kao fontovi. Možete odrediti njihovu veličinu pomoću piksela, a one će uzeti veličinu fonta od svog roditeljskog HTML elementa.</p>\n<p>Možete uključiti Font Awesome u bilo koju aplikaciju dodavanjem sledećeg koda na vašu HTML datoteku:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.8.1/css/all.css\" integrity=\"sha384-50oBUHEmvpQ+1lW4y57PTFmhCaXp0ML5d60M1M7uH2+nqUivzIebhndOJK28anvf\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n</code></pre>\n<p>U ovom slučaju, već smo ga za vas dodali na ovu stranicu tajno.</p>\n<p>Element <code>&#x3C;i></code> je prvobitno korišćen za formatiranje teksta u kurziv, ali se sada često koristi i za ikone. Možete dodati klase Font Awesome na element <code>&#x3C;i></code> kako biste ga pretvorili u ikonu, na primer:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;i class=\"fas fa-info-circle\">&#x3C;/i>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Zapamtite da je i element <code>&#x3C;span></code> prihvatljiv za korišćenje za ikone.</p>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aedd08845","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Koristite Font Awesome da dodate ikonu <code>thumbs-up</code> na vaše dugme za \"Like\" dajući elementu <code>&#x3C;i></code> klase <code>fas</code> i <code>fa-thumbs-up</code>. Uverite se da ostavljate tekst \"Like\" pored ikone.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16638,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/add-font-awesome-icons-to-our-buttons"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null},{"link":"https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.8.1/css/all.css","src":null}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lobster\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\r\n<style>\r\n  h2 {\r\n    font-family: Lobster, Monospace;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .thick-green-border {\r\n    border-color: green;\r\n    border-width: 10px;\r\n    border-style: solid;\r\n    border-radius: 50%;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-8\">\r\n      <h2 class=\"text-primary text-center\">CatPhotoApp</h2>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n      <a href=\"#\"><img class=\"img-responsive thick-green-border\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Tuxedo cats running on dirt ground.\">\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n      <button class=\"btn btn-block btn-primary\">Like</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n      <button class=\"btn btn-block btn-info\">Info</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n      <button class=\"btn btn-block btn-danger\">Delete</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <p>Things cats <span class=\"text-danger\">love:</span></p>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>catnip</li>\r\n    <li>laser pointers</li>\r\n    <li>lasagna</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <p>Top 3 things cats hate:</p>\r\n  <ol>\r\n    <li>flea treatment</li>\r\n    <li>thunder</li>\r\n    <li>other cats</li>\r\n  </ol>\r\n  <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\r\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Indoor</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Loving</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Lazy</label>\r\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Crazy</label>\r\n    <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\r\n    <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\r\n  </form>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da dodate element <code>&#x3C;i></code> sa klasama <code>fas</code> i <code>fa-thumbs-up</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelector('i')?.classList?.value === 'fas fa-thumbs-up' || document.querySelector('span')?.classList?.value === 'fas fa-thumbs-up');"},{"text":"<p>Vaša ikona <code>fa-thumbs-up</code> treba da bude unutar dugmeta za \"Like\".</p>","testString":"const iconTextContent = document.querySelector('i.fa-thumbs-up')?.parentNode?.textContent;  \r\nconst spanTextContent = document.querySelector('span.fa-thumbs-up')?.parentNode?.textContent;  \r\nassert.isTrue(\r\n  (iconTextContent?.match(/Like/gi) &&\r\n    document.querySelector('.btn-primary > i') === document.querySelector('.fas.fa-thumbs-up')) ||\r\n    (spanTextContent?.match(/Like/gi) &&\r\n      document.querySelector('.btn-primary > span') === document.querySelector('.fas.fa-thumbs-up')));"},{"text":"<p>Vaš element <code>&#x3C;i></code> treba da ima tekst \"Like\" pored sebe.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /(<\\/i>|<\\/span>)\\s*Like\\s*<\\/button>/g);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/#bootstrap","dashedName":"add-font-awesome-icons-to-our-buttons","certifi